* Iron Raptor watched as prowl had gathered Zenyak and flown off towards the base, she had felt his gears tense when she had touched him and wondered if something was bothering him. She looked down at her thumb, Prowl's mech fluid staining it and occasionally dripping onto the ground below. With a sigh she wiped the fluid on a leaf of a near by tree and then looked up as Prowl was beginning to disappear in the distance.
She had to catch up.*

" Beast Mode!"

* Now in the most familiar form she knew Iron Raptor began to run off towards the Ark, Prowl's form becoming more and more destiguishable with every stride.
It wouldn't be long until both of them would get back to the Ark, but what would they do with Zenyak then?
She guessed that they would just have to wait and see.*
